dct_title_s: Madrid y su entorno : MTN50 / Ministerio de Transportes, Movilidad y Agenda Urbana ; producción e impresión Instituto Grográfico Nacional.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights. SGR80 ellipsoid. UTM projection. Datum ETRS89. The longitudes are referred to the Greenwich meridian. The altitudes refer to the average level of the Mediterranean in Alicante. Equidistances contour lines is 20 meters. The coordinates in dark blue correspond to the UTM ETRS89 kilometer grid. The coordinates in light blue correspond to the start of the UTM ED50 grid. Includes land cover, diagram of administrative divisions, municipal codes and names, toponymy, geodetic vertices network are listed.
dct_publisher_sm: Madrid Instituto Geográfico Nacional. Subdirección General de Geodesia y Cartografía 2020.
